Re: Wikileaks contact info?

Bitcointalk

2010-12-05 09:08:08 UTC - [11]Original Post

   [12]Quote from: RHorning on December 04, 2010, 10:17:44 PM
   Basically, bring it on.  Letʼs encourage Wikileaks to use Bitcoins and
   Iʼm willing to face any risk or fallout from that act.
   No, donʼt "bring it on".
   The project needs to grow gradually so the software can be strengthened
   along the way.
   I make this appeal to WikiLeaks not to try to use Bitcoin.  Bitcoin is
   a small beta community in its infancy.  You would not stand to get more
   than pocket change, and the heat you would bring would likely destroy
   us at this stage.
